ygData.messageBody:
Hello all once again! My Character's name is
Lenexa and is an officer to the guild Semper Vigilans. I
was wondering if any of you fine people play on my
server...Solusek Ro. If so you can leave a message here or e-mail
me at wyld_wyvern@... <br> I look forward
to hearing from you and who knows...may be
recruiting you into my guild..:)<br>(or you can just look me
up in game)<br> Oh, btw, My character just got
married last friday at 12:30 pm and boy was it
cool!!!<br> any way, go well my friends and good
hunting!<br><br>Wyld-Wyvern/Lenexa 11lvl enc Solusek Ro-Semper Vigilans
